title: Crime Patrol - क्राइम पेट्रोल सतर्क - Episode 547 - 22nd August, 2015
description:
Aamir is in control of Sakeena and obliges to every instruction given by her. Worried parents of Aamir seek help of Police and ultimately Sakeena gets arrested for her heinous crimes. Meanwhile, a girl named Kajal is missing from her home and her parents has lodged the complaint of their missing child. Can Kajal be found? Who took her? To know all, watch the full episode.

Click to watch all the episodes of Crime Patrol - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzufeTFnhupza0aEZ_FKj0mBguCdtwU_c

Crime Patrol coming back in its 4th season attempts to bring stories of crime happening all around the country. Crimes that tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved.Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, “It should not have happened”.Would knowing the “Why” behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?“I don’t like the way he looks at me”, “I don’t like the way he/she is behaving”, “I think he/she is out of his/her mind”, “I think he/she has gone crazy”. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare which unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there.In a house a husband and wife argue, fight. A vessel comes flying, a glass breaks. Husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance that keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there.Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy.Crime Patrol- Dastak will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. May be, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: Crime Patrol - Discontented - Episode 412 - 5th September 2014
description:
Ep 412 - Crime Patrol Satark - In this UP special episode of Crime Patrol Satark, Host Anoop Soni explores the story of 2 Families who go through the same pain of losing one of their loved ones from their Family. Jagdish's Friend Lalit requests him to settle down as he lost his Wife Prerna and also talks about Sarita a divorcee who lost her Child. Jagdish's Father and Prerna get murdered. Who killed them? When this incident occurred in the house, nobody was there accept 2 labors, 2 people who came to meet Babuji and Sarita. Watch to find out. Watch all the latest videos of Crime Patrol Satark online on SonyLiv official website SonyLiv.com.

"Crime Patrol coming back in its 4th season attempts to bring stories of crime happening all around the country. Crimes that tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved.Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, “It should not have happened”.Would knowing the “Why” behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?“I don’t like the way he looks at me”, “I don’t like the way he/she is behaving”, “I think he/she is out of his/her mind”, “I think he/she has gone crazy”. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare which unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there.In a house a husband and wife argue, fight. A vessel comes flying, a glass breaks. Husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance that keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there.Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy.Crime Patrol- Dastak will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. May be, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

description:

#shorts #anime #dbz #naruto #demonslayer #broly #vegeta #tiktok #goku #akiratoriyama 
#gwilly #gwillyyt #purpysage #imtracyallen #DBHype #polyanime #finalform15


A powerful fox known as the Nine-Tails attacks Konoha, the hidden leaf village in the Land of Fire, one of the Five Great Shinobi Countries in the Ninja World. In response, the leader of Konoha and the Fourth Hokage, Minato Namikaze seals the fox inside the body of his newborn son, Naruto Uzumaki, making Naruto a host of the beast;[i] this costs Naruto's father his life, and the Third Hokage returns from retirement to become the leader of Konoha again. Naruto is often scorned by Konoha's villagers for being the host of the Nine-Tails. Due to a decree by the Third Hokage forbidding any mention of these events, Naruto learns nothing about the Nine-Tails until 12 years later, when Mizuki, a renegade ninja, reveals the truth to Naruto. Naruto then defeats Mizuki in combat, earning the respect of his teacher, Iruka Umino.[ii]

Shortly afterward, Naruto becomes a ninja and joins with Sasuke Uchiha, against whom he often competes, and Sakura Haruno, on whom he has a crush, to form Team 7, under an experienced sensei, the elite ninja Kakashi Hatake. Like all the ninja teams from every village, Team 7 completes missions requested by the villagers, ranging from doing chores and being bodyguards to performing assassinations.

After several missions, including a major one in the Land of Waves, Kakashi allows Team 7 to take a ninja exam, enabling them to advance to a higher rank and take on more difficult missions, known as Chunin Exams. During the exams, Orochimaru, a wanted criminal, invades Konoha and kills the Third Hokage for revenge. Jiraiya, one of the three legendary ninjas, declines the title of Fifth Hokage and searches with Naruto for Tsunade whom he chooses to become Fifth Hokage instead.

During the search, it is revealed that Orochimaru wishes to train Sasuke because of his powerful genetic heritage, the Sharingan. [iii] After Sasuke attempts and fails to kill his older brother Itachi,[iv] who had showed up in Konoha to kidnap Naruto, he joins Orochimaru, hoping to gain from him the strength needed to kill Itachi. The story takes a turn when Sasuke leaves the village: Tsunade sends a group of ninja, including Naruto, to retrieve Sasuke, but Naruto is unable to persuade or force him to come back. Naruto and Sakura do not give up on Sasuke; Naruto leaves Konoha to receive training from Jiraiya to prepare himself for the next time he encounters Sasuke, while Sakura becomes Tsunade's apprentice.

Part II
See also: List of Naruto chapters (Part II, volumes 28–48) and List of Naruto chapters (Part II, 

#love 
Two and a half years later, Naruto returns from his training with Jiraiya. The Akatsuki starts kidnapping the hosts of the powerful Tailed Beasts. Team 7 and other Leaf ninja fight against them and search for their teammate Sasuke. The Akatsuki succeeds in capturing and extracting seven of the Tailed Beasts, killing all the hosts except Gaara, who is now the Kazekage. Meanwhile, Sasuke betrays Orochimaru and faces Itachi to take revenge. After Itachi dies in battle, Sasuke learns from the Akatsuki founder Tobi that Itachi had been ordered by Konoha's superiors to destroy his clan to prevent a coup; he accepted, on the condition that Sasuke would be spared. Devastated by this revelation, Sasuke joins the Akatsuki to destroy Konoha in revenge. As Konoha ninjas defeat several Akatsuki members, the Akatsuki figurehead leader, Nagato, kills Jiraiya and devastates Konoha, but Naruto defeats and redeems him, earning the village's respect and admiration.

With Nagato's death, Tobi, disguised as Madara Uchiha (one of Konoha's founding fathers), announces that he wants to capture all nine Tailed Beasts to cast an illusion powerful enough to control all humanity and achieve world peace. The leaders of the five ninja villages refuse to help him and instead join forces to confront his faction and allies. That decision results in a Fourth Shinobi World War between the combined armies of the Five Great Countries (known as the Allied Shinobi Forces) and Akatsuki's forces of zombie-like ninjas. The Five Kage try to keep Naruto, unaware of the war, in a secret island turtle near Kumogakure (Hidden Cloud Village), but Naruto finds out and escapes from the island with Killer Bee, the host of the Eight-Tails. At that time, Naruto—along with the help of Killer Bee—gains control of his Tailed Beast and the two of them head for the battlefield.

title: Awaaz Desh Ki : Cyber Crime | साइबर अपराध | 18 December, 2022
description:
संसद टीवी के ख़ास कार्यक्रम 'आवाज देश की' में आज बात साइबर अपराध की. देश में तेजी से साइबर अपराधों का चलन बढ़ रहा हैं. साइबर अपराध के बढ़ते मामलों की पीछे कारण क्या हैं, और इसे रोकने के लिए हमारे पास क्या व्यवस्थाएं हैं.. सरकार या राज्यों इसे कैसे अपनाते हैं और चुनौतियां क्या हैं, एक आम आदमी के पास क्या विकल्प हैं. पिछले तीन सालों में साइबर अपराध की प्रति दिन 1500 घटनाएं सामने आईं हैं, जनवरी, 2020 से 7 दिसंबर, 2022 तक 16 लाख मामले दर्ज हुए, 32,000 से अधिक मामलों में एफआईआर दर्ज की गई, नेशनल साइबर क्राइम रिपोर्टिंग पोर्टल पर दर्ज 98 फीसदी मामले दर्ज ही नहीं हुए वही RBI के अनुसार 2020-21 में प्राइवेट बैंक के ग्राहकों के साथ 1.38 लाख करोड़ रुपए का फ्रॉड हुआ,एनसीआरबी के आंकड़ों के मुताबिक, 2018 में कुल 21,796 मामले दर्ज किये थे जो अब बढ़कर 50,035 हो गए हैं. आम लोगों से लेकर मशहूर हस्तियां साइबर क्राइम का शिकार हो रही हैं एम्स के सर्वर पर साइबर अटैक बढ़ते साइबर क्राइम का ही नमूना है. साइबर अपराध पूरे देश में एक प्रमुख मुद्दा बनकर उभरा है, ऐसे में, अपराध भौगोलिक सीमाओं को पार कर जाते हैं जिससे अपराधियों को ट्रैक करना मुश्किल हो जाता है. जालसाज जहां भोले-भाले लोगों को ठगने के लिए नए-नए तरीके खोजते रहते हैं, वहीं यह पुलिस के लिए भी एक बड़ी चुनौती बन गई है. सरकारी आंकड़े साइबर क्राइम के बढ़ते चलन की ओर इशारा करते हैं.. तो बात इन्हीं मुद्दों की.

Guests:-
1. Brijesh Singh, Additional Director General of Police, Govt. of Maharashtra
      बृजेश सिंह, अतिरिक्त महानिदेशक, महाराष्ट्र पुलिस

2. Dr. Charru Malhotra, Professor, e-Governance & ICT, Indian Institute of Public Administration
       डॉ. चारू मल्होत्रा, प्रोफेसर, भारतीय लोक प्रशासन संस्थान (IIPA)

3. Dr. Pavan Duggal, Advocate, Supreme Court of India/Founder & Chairman, International     Commission on Cyber Security Law

title: Supreme Court में केंद्र की अर्जी, Armed Forces में Adultery को अपराध ही रहने दें | वनइंडिया हिंदी
description:
The Supreme Court on Wednesday agreed to examine the Central government’s plea urging to exempt the Armed forces from the purview of its 2018 judgment of decriminalizing the criminal offense of adultery. The matter has been sent to the Chief Justice of India for listing it before a five-judge bench.

सुप्रीम कोर्ट ने सशस्त्र बलों के लिए अडल्टरी यानी व्याभिचार को अपराध मानने के लिए केंद्र सरकार के याचिका की जांच करने के लिए बुधवार सहमति व्यक्त की. शीर्ष अदालत की एक बेंच ने चीफ जस्टिस ऑफ इंडिया से अनुरोध किया कि वे केंद्र की याचिका पर स्पष्टीकरण जारी करने के लिए पांच न्यायाधीशों की संविधान पीठ गठित करें. सितंबर 2018 में, सुप्रीम कोर्ट ने 158 साल पुराने कानून को रद्द कर दिया था जिसके तहत भारत में व्यभिचार अपराध था.

title: اختفاء بهلول أثناء العاصفة التي كانت في اذربيجان | العشق الممنوع الحلقة 34
description:
السيدة فردوس هي واحدة من عائلة السيد مليح.  لديها إبنتان. في يوم من الأيام ، بسبب سلوكها غير الأخلاقي مات زوجها بسبب أزمة.
 بنات السيدة فردوس هما بهتيار و بيكار. بناتها تكبران بمرور الوقت وتتزوج بيكار. السيدة فردوس وبناتها يولون أهمية كبيرة ليبدو جميلين. السيدة فردوس تريد الزواج من السيد عدنان. السيد عدنان هو واحد من أغنى الناس في تلك الفترة. لكن السيد عدنان يريد بهتيار. تعارض السيدة فردوس هذا الزواج في البداية ، ولكن عليها أن تقبله. السيد عدنان لديه طفلان ،  نيهال 12 سنة. و بولنت  يبلغ من العمر حوالي 6 سنوات. فقد عدنان زوجته عندما كان  بولنت صغيراً. نيهال تبدوغير مسرورة لهذا الزواج. ولكن عندما تلتقي ببهتيار ، تصبح دافئة في الداخل. بهتياربدأت تشعر بالملل خلال عامين من هذا الزواج.العلاقة بينهما بدأت تفسد.

title: Suspected serial killer pleads not guilty to 1998 cold case murder

title: Doorbraak in cold case-zaak? ‘Dit is een van grotere mysteries’
description:
Dankzij een dna-match is vrijdag een verdachte opgepakt voor de moord op Els Slurink in 1997. Door nieuwe technieken kon een bruikbaar dna-profiel gemaakt worden wat leidde tot de arrestatie. Misdaadverslaggever Mick van Wely legt uit dat er steeds meer mogelijk is om daders van cold case-zaken op te sporen. De advocaat van de verdachte, Peter Plasman, heeft laten weten vooralsnog niet te kunnen reageren op de aanhouding. Zijn cliënt zit in beperkingen vast. title: Peter Perjesy Vermisst seit dem 22-September 1981. Cold Case Schweiz - Ein rätselhaftes Verschwinden
description:
Am 22.September 1981 kam Peter Perjesy aus Wattwil-Ulisbach nach einem abendlichen Tischtennis-Training im Schulhaus Risi nie zuhause an.
Die einzige Spur, die vom damals 14-Jährigen blieb, waren sein Velo sowie seine Jacke. Trotz umfangreicher Suche in der ganzen Gegend blieb er bis heute spurlos verschwunden. Die Ungewissheit über das Schicksal einer verschwunden Person ist für die Angehörigen besonders quälend. Es sei ein Wechselbad der Gefühle, beschrieb es seine Mutter gegenüber einer Reporterin.
Sie lebt heute im St. Galler Oberland. «Mit dem Tod kann man abschliessen, man kann an ein Grab gehen oder ein Ritual machen.» Aber wenn die Person nie gefunden werde, könne man nichts machen, um den Verlust zu bewältigen. Es bleibt ein Wechselbad von Hoffen, Resignieren und Trauern. Man komme dabei auf die wildesten Spekulationen, erzählt eine andere Mutter eines Vermissten.
Hinweise sind an die Kantonspolizei Thurgau per Tel. 052 728 22 22 (Ausland 41 52 728 22 22), per Mail oder an jede Polizeidienststelle zu richten. SRF Beitrag 2013 - Hier hochgeladen gegen das Vergessen.

A 16-year-old girl died after she was stabbed over 40 times by her boyfriend in the Shahbad dairy area in the Outer North District of Delhi on Sunday. The grisly murder was caught on CCTV.

title: Murder Capital of the World | Living in San Pedro Sula, Honduras | Free Documentary
description:
Murder Capital of the World | Living in San Pedro Sula, Honduras | Free Documentary

World's Most Feared Gang in Guatemala - Meet the Maras: https://youtu.be/ymS1fMM9wB8

In the company of a pastor, an assassin, and a crime reporter, this film examines the fine line between good and evil in the world's most dangerous city.

Priest and furniture maker Daniel Pacheco works in one of the most dangerous cities in the world: San Pedro Sula, Honduras. He tries to save lives, but that’s no simple matter in a country with staggeringly high murder rates. The killings are countless, not just by the drug cartels but also by the police and the army. Pacheco lives in the midst of it, risking his own life.

Reporting murders is everyday business for TV journalist Orlin Castro. He seems comfortable with the nocturnal violence, but at the same time, he dreams of a different, quieter life. A hitman named Matathan talks openly about his profession. He says he has had enough and wants to start a new, pious existence. But Pacheco, who knows him well, doubts his sincerity.

Following these three men, Dutch-American filmmaker Loretta van der Horst, who was born in Honduras, gets frighteningly close to the horrific violence that no one seems able to end. If you don’t value your own life, Pacheco explains, it’s easier to kill others.

About The CID :
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows.  Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman, played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam along with Daya and Abhijit. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

भारतीय टेलीविजन पर पहली रोमांचक खोजी श्रृंखला आज सबसे लोकप्रिय शो में से एक है। नाटकीय और बिल्कुल अप्रत्याशित, सी.आई.डी. पिछले ग्यारह वर्षों में दर्शकों को मंत्रमुग्ध कर दिया है और अपने रोमांचक कथानक और उत्साह से दर्शकों को उनके टेलीविजन सेटों से बांधे रखा है। इसके तेज़-तर्रार कथानकों में सी.आई.डी. की व्यक्तिगत चुनौतियाँ भी गुंथी हुई हैं। टीम को ड्यूटी के नाम पर बिना रुके साहसिक कार्य, जबरदस्त दबाव और जोखिम का सामना करना पड़ता है। श्रृंखला में जांच, पता लगाने और रहस्य से संबंधित कठोर पुलिस प्रक्रियात्मक कहानियां शामिल हैं। धारावाहिक के नायक पुलिस बल के अपराध जांच विभाग से संबंधित पुलिस अधिकारियों का एक विशिष्ट समूह हैं, जिसका नेतृत्व एसीपी प्रद्युम्न कर रहे हैं, जिनकी भूमिका दया और अभिजीत के साथ गतिशील शिवाजी सातम ने निभाई है। हालाँकि कहानियाँ विश्वसनीय हैं, लेकिन इसमें नाटकीय कथानक और पुलिस द्वारा सामना की जाने वाली तकनीकी जटिलताओं पर भी जोर दिया गया है। हर चरण में, कथानक में दिलचस्प मोड़ आते हैं और अधिकारी छोटे-छोटे सुरागों के आधार पर अपराधियों का पता लगाने में सक्रिय रहते हैं।

مسلسل إختفاء نيللى كريم 2018 تدور الأحداث حول دكتورة جامعية في روسيا، وتعيش مع زوجها هناك، لكن فجأة وبدون مقدمات يختفي زوجها، لتبدأ رحلة البحث عنه، ويصل بها الأمر للعودة إلى مصر في إطار رحلة بحثها، لكن هذه الرحلة تفاجئها بالكثير من الأمور التي لم تكن على علم بها.
مسلسل إختفاء بطولة- نيللي كريم - محمد ممدوح - بسمة - هشام سليم - سيف هنو - إسماعيل شرف - محمد علاء - رانيا منصور - أحمد صبرى غباشي 
إخراج: أحمد مدحت (مخرج)  رضا عبدالرازق 
تأليف: أيمن مدحت 
إنتاج - العدل جروب El Adl Group 
تصنيف العمل: غموض - تشويق وإثارة 
مسلسل إختفاء يعد العمل الخامس لنيللى كريم مع العدل جروب Al Adl Group وهم 
مسلسل سجن النسا, تحت السيطرة, سقوط حر , لأعلى سعر , إختفاء. 
كانت أخر أعمال النجمة نيللى كريم فى رمضان 2018 مسلسل لأعلى سعر من إنتاج العدل جروب

title: Agression raciste à Cergy : le livreur victime témoigne
description: L'agression raciste d'un jeune livreur Uber Eats à Cergy, dans le Val-d'Oise, dimanche soir, a fait le tour des réseaux sociaux. Alors qu'il attendait une commande devant le restaurant Brasco, Joseph est pris à partie, puis frappé et insulté par un homme encapuchonné. Il revient sur son agression sur BFMTV. Le ton hésitant, pansement collé sur le front, Joseph raconte comment les faits se sont déroulés. En attendant une commande, le livreur noir écoute de la musique sur une enceinte. Un homme l'interpelle et lui demande d'éteindre sa musique. « Par gentillesse, je descends le volume de mon enceinte. Ça lui suffisait pas », relate Joseph. « Il a dit : “Il faut descendre.” J'ai refusé. » https://www.lepoint.fr/societe/agression-raciste-a-cergy-le-livreur-victime-temoigne-01-06-2021-2429074_23.php Suivez nous sur : - Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/c/lepoint/ - Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/lepoint.fr/ - Twitter : https://twitter.com/LePoint - Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/lepointfr - www.lepoint.fr

title: Représailles après les attaques sexuelles à Cologne : Agression de 6 Pakistanais et 1 Syrien
description:
Abonnez-vous à notre chaîne sur YouTube : http://f24.my/youtube
En DIRECT - Suivez FRANCE 24 ici : http://f24.my/YTliveFR

En Allemagne, l'onde de choc du scandale des attaques sexuelles du jour de l'an... et les 1eres représailles... ce matin, la police signale l'agression de 6 Pakistanais et d'un Syrien par des inconnus dimanche dans le centre de Cologne. Les étrangers montrés du doigt. Parmi les 19 suspects des agressions du 1er janvier figurent des réfugiés. Le mouvement Pégida exploite la séquence.

title: OKCPD Cold Case: Helen Gordon #shorts
description:
Raped. Beaten. Murdered. This was the tragic fate that ended 77 year-old Helen Gordon's life. Christmas Eve of 1975, Helen was with her family but never made it home. Her body was found two days later. The Oklahoma City Police Department has never given up on her case. OKCPD asks for your help. If you know anything, she and her family still deserve justice. 

Tips can be submitted to OKCPD anonymously through Crime Stoppers (405) 235-7300.

https://okccrimetips.com

التعريف بالقناة:
تهتم قناتنا بحصر كل أنواع الجريمة وأصنافها ،من جرائم القتل ،وجرائم السرقة ،وجرائم الإغتصاب، و جرائم السطو المسلح،  وجرائم سرقة  البنوك، و جرائم النصب والإحتيال ،والبركاج، والهروب من السجون، نقدم كل هاته الجرائم في قالب خاص به نوع من الحبكة والتشويق،  هذفنا من كل هذا هو تبيان بأن الجريمة لا تجدي،  و أن المجرم مهما طال به الامد في عيش الحرية إلا أن مآله السجن والعقاب. كما أن المفاد من ذلك هو توعية الناس و حثهم على أخذ الحيطة والحذر في تعاملهم من الناس الأقربين إليهم و الغرباء ايضا. نأمل ان ينال إعجابكم محتوانا ولا تبخلوا علينا بالإشتراك والإعجاب حال أعجبكم المحتوى،  سننشر المقاطع بشكل دوري.

Bangladesh MP's Murder In India: How Killers ‘Tricked’ Police To Escape Crime Spot? Shocking Details
description:
Some shocking details in the murder case of a Bangladeshi MP in India have emerged. The accused in custody shared how they escaped from the crime spot. After killing MP Anwarul Azim Anar in a flat in Kolkata, the suspected murderers reportedly left the spot wearing his clothes. Anar’s murder came to the fore last week, days after the leader went missing in Kolkata. CCTV footage showed the killers leaving the apartment in New Town with plastic bags and a trolley bag that allegedly contained the chopped  body parts of the Bangladeshi lawmaker.

title: ترتيب الدول حسب معدل جرائم القتل🔪| معدلات الجريمة في العالم😰
description:
وفقًا لبحث أجراه مكتب الأمم المتحدة المعني بالمخدرات والجريمة ، فإن أمريكا الوسطى هي المكان الأكثر خطورة للعيش فيه ، حيث يوجد 62.1 جريمة قتل - أو عمليات قتل غير قانونية - لكل 100 ألف حالة وفاة في بعض "المناطق الساخنة".
كانت آسيا وأوروبا وأوقيانوسيا (التي تضم أستراليا وميلانيزيا وميكرونيزيا وبولينيزيا) أكثر البلدان أمانًا للعيش من حيث عدد جرائم القتل الأقل ، حيث سجلت 2.3 و 3.0 و 2.8 جريمة قتل لكل 100 ألف حالة وفاة على التوالي ، أي أقل بكثير من المتوسط العالمي. 6.1 جرائم.
وفقًا لدراسة جرائم القتل العالمية لعام 2019 ، كان معدل جرائم القتل في إفريقيا 13.0 ، وهو أقل من معدل جرائم القتل في الأمريكيتين (17.2) ، والتي سجلت أعلى معدلات في عام 2017 منذ بدء التسجيل وجمع البيانات في عام 1990. ومع ذلك ، يشير التقرير أيضًا إلى أن البيانات التي تم الحصول عليها في العديد من الدول الأفريقية لديها فجوات كبيرة.

الفيديو التالي هوعبارة عن إحصائيات حول موضوع ترتيب الدول حسب معدل جرائم القتل 2021، حيث يظهر الفيديو في تسلسل زمني ترتيب عدد ضحايا جرائم القتل لكل 100k

بحثنا في هذا الفيديو في كل من العناوين التالية:
- الدول حسب معدل جريمة القتل العالمي
- قائمة الدول حسب معدل جرائم القتل
- أخطر الدول في الاتحاد الأوروبي
- جرائم القتل العمد (لكل 100 ألف شخص) 
- ترتيب الدول من حيث معدل الجريمة
- أكثر الدول اجراما في العالم
-أخطر جرائم القتل في العالم
- أكثر الدول إجراماً في العالم 2021

title: مهمة خاصة "جرائم الشرف في كردستان العراق"
description:
قبورٌ بدونَ أسماء، أرقامٌ وشواهدُ هِي مقابرُ لنساءٍ قُتِلْنَ بدافعِ ما يعرف بجرائم الشَّرَفِ في #كردستان #العراق، وبحسْبِ مديريَّةِ مُكافحةِ العُنْفِ ضِدَّ الأسرةِ والمرأة، فإنَّ النساءَ في كردستان العراق يتعرَّضْنَ للانتهاكِ بشكلٍ مُنَظَّم، ولَمْ يمرْ عامٌ منذُ العام 1992 من دون أن تتعرَّضَ النساءُ للعنفِ أو القتلِ بدافعِ الشَّرَف. فريق #العربية تقصّى عن القضايَا المتعلقةِ بجرائمِ الشَّرف، بخاصة #جرائم_العنف و #القتل المُرتبِطةِ بغِشَاءِ العذرية حيث تختلف أساليب القتل ويبقى السبب واحدا هو دافع الشرف .
معاناةُ الضحيَّةِ لا تنتهِي بعدَ مقتلِهَا، بل تستمرُّ بعدَ ذلكَ، فرجل الدين يرفضُ تلقينَهُنَّ، كَمَا ترفضُ النِّسْوَةُ غسل جثامين الضحايا لاعتقادِهِنَّ بأنَّ الوَصْمَةَ لا تُغْسَل. منذُ العامِ 2012 حتَّى عامِ 2021 ، سُجِّلَتْ أربعةُ آلافٍ وأربعَ عشرةَ  حادثةَ عُنفٍ ضِدَّ النساءِ، تشملُ القتلَ والحَرْقَ والانتحار. غشاءَ البِكارةِ هوَ أحدُ الأسبابِ الرئيسة لجرائمِ القتلِ في المجتمعِ العراقي المحافظ. ولا تُعدُّ مهمَّةُ اللَّجنةِ الحكوميَّةِ الطبيَّةِ سهلةً بسببِ الانتقاداتِ التِي تتعرَّضُ لَهَا مِن طرفِ المجتمعِ المدنيّ، والمنظماتِ النَّسَوِيةِ، التي تعتبرُ أنَّ الكشفَ عَنْ بِكَارة المرأةِ هوَ إهانةٌ لَهَا. بالرغمِ مِن القوانينَ المشدَّدَةِ، إلَّا أنَّها لمْ تتمكّنْ مِن إيقافِ جرائمِ القتلِ والعُنْفِ ضدَّ المرأة، ولا يفيدُ تقريرُ اللِّجانِ، الذِي يُثْبِتُ في الكثيرِ مِن الأحيانِ أنَّ الضَّحِيَّةَ مَا زالتْ بكرًا في إنقاذِ حياتِهَا، فالعائلةُ تَبقَى مُصِّرةً عَلَى تنفيذِ القتلِ. وتعودُ أسبابُ الإصرارِ علَى تنفيذِ القتلِ إلى عدمِ قَبولِ الأهالِي بنتائجِ اللِّجانِ بخصوصِ عذرية الفتاة، ولجوءِ كثيرين مِنْهُم إلى أطباءٍ مَحليينَ غيرِ مخوَّلِينَ مِن طرفِ الحكومةِ بإعطاءِ التَّقَارير، لتحديدِ عُذْرِيَّةِ الفتاة من عدمها. تُجْبَرُ الضحيَّةُ على الذِّهابِ إلى لجنةِ كشفِ العذريَّةِ يرافقُهَا أهلُهَا وعائلةُ زوجِهَا لمعرفةِ القرارِ الذِي سيُحدِّدُ مصيرَهَا. 
غالبية النساءِ اللواتي يتمُّ قتلُهُنَّ في مجتمعاتِنا ولأسباب ودوافع مختلفة، يتمُّ وصمُهنَّ وتحويرُ سبَبِ القتلِ إلى دافعِ الشرفِ. وتستبعد الأسبابِ الجنائية والاجتماعيّةِ أو الانتحارِ والمُشْكِلات الأُخرَى. فمتى يتوقف قتل النساء في العراق ؟

title: रिश्तों का एक Complex मायाजाल | Crime Patrol | Inspector Series
description:
Click here to Subscribe to SET India: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Priya, who was stalked by Jitendra, is missing. Jitendra, known for his charm, is the prime suspect. On the other hand, Babli, a 12-year-old chirpy girl, too is missing. On investigation, Jitendra’s innocence is proved, and Babli turns out to be related to Priya. This creates a lot of confusion for the police, who are caught in an inter-related web of suspects. Will they unravel the mystery before the criminal escapes?

Show Name: Crime Patrol Satark Season 2
Host: Anup Soni
Producers: Prem Krishen Malhotra, Sunil Mehta, Vipul D. Shah, Anirban Bhattacharyya

#crimepatrol #क्राइमपेट्रोल #setindia #क्राइमपट्रोलसतर्क #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrol #crime #thrillers #CP #क्राइमपैट्रॉलसतर्क #livcrime #crimepatroldastak #crimepatroldial100 #anupsoni #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrolfullepisode #crimepatrollatestepisode #crimepatrolnewepisode #crimepatroldial100 #crimepatrol2024 #crimepatrolserial #crimepatrolbestepisode #crimepatrolsony #crimepatrolnewepisode #bestcrimepatrolepisode #crimepatrolmostpopularepisode #क्राइमपेट्रोल #crimepatrolcases #crimeworld #crimeworld2024 #crimeworldnewepisode #crimeworldbestepisode #crimeworldfullepisode #indiancrime #indiancrimestories

About Crime Patrol : 
-----------------------------------
Crimes tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved. Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, 'It should not have happened. Would knowing the 'Why' behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?' I don’t like the way he looks at me', 'I don’t like the way he/she is behaving', 'I think he/she is out of his/her mind', 'I think he/she has gone crazy'. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare that unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there. In a house a husband and wife argue, and fight. A vessel comes flying, and a glass breaks. The husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there. Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy. Crime Patrol - Satark Rahe will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. Maybe, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately, after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: कोई भी काम अपराध कैसे बनता है | अपराध के चरण हैं | Different Stages of Crime
description:
Different Stages of Crime | Essential Elements of Crime

आज की इस video में हम बात करेंगे अपराध के कितने चरण होते हैं। किसी भी एक कार्य को अपराध का रूप लेने के लिए किन चरण से हो कर गुजरना पड़ता है।
-
जब कोई अपराध का कार्य कारित करता है तब वो कार्य अनेक चरणों से होकर अपराध का रूप लेता है। अपराध को मुख्य चार चरणों में बाटा जाता हैं। और वो चरण हैं–
1. पहला आशय यानि इरादा (intention),
2. दूसरा तैयारी (Preparation),
3. तीसरा प्रयास (Attempt) और
4. चौथा और आखरी है  अपराध का निष्पादन (Accomplishment Or Completion)
 ......................... For More Details Please Watch Full Video

विधि के अंतर्गत यह एक महत्वपूर्ण विषय है और इसके विषय में संपूर्ण ज्ञान होना अत्यंत आवश्यक है। आज अपराधी को नहीं बल्कि अपराध का अंत करने का भरपूर प्रयास किया जाता है और अपराधी व्यक्ति की मनोदशा यानि उसके मानसिक स्थिति में सुधार किया जाता है। जिससे स्वच्छ और सुरक्षित समाज का विकास हो सके।


दण्ड क्या है और दण्ड के प्रकार?
इसके बारे में जानकारी हो गई होगी। उम्मीद करता हूँ हमारे द्वारा दी गई जानकारी से आप संतुष्ट होंगे। अगर फिर भी इससे सम्बन्धित या अन्य किसी भी प्रकार की कुछ भी शंका आपके मन में हो या अन्य कोई जानकारी प्राप्त करना चाहते है, तो आप  हमें  कमेंट  बॉक्स  के  माध्यम  से अपने प्रश्न और सुझाव हमें भेज सकते है अगर इससे भी और अधिक जानकारी आप जानना चाहते हैं तो हमें कमेंट बॉक्स में कमेंट कर के जरूर बताएं। अगर आप हमारे द्वारा दी गई जानकारी में कोई गलती पाते हैं तो वह जरूर कमेंट करके हमें बताएं। ताकि हम आगे आने वाली Video में एक बेहतरीन सुधार के साथ आपको बेहतरीन जानकारी दे सकें। इसको अपने मित्रो के साथ शेयर जरूर करें।

title: Ukraine : un tribunal international pour sanctionner le crime d’agression ? • FORUM • TRAD FR
description:
L’Ukraine et à sa suite, la Commission européenne militent pour la création d’un Tribunal spécial pour sanctionner le crime d’agression contre l’Ukraine. Depuis les tribunaux de Nuremberg, l’agression est considéré comme « le crime des crimes », mais il n’a jamais été poursuivi. La Cour pénale internationale qui enquête sur les crimes de guerre en Ukraine n’a pas de compétence pour poursuivre le crime d’agression. Les partisans d’un tel tribunal spécial considèrent que celui-ci pourrait créer un important précédent pour sanctionner les guerres d’agression. Les sceptiques mettent en garde sur le fait qu’un tel tribunal viendrait consacrer une justice internationale sélective qui ne sanctionnerait que les pariahs.

En partenariat avec Médecins Sans Frontières, l’Organisation mondiale contre la torture et ARTE

Intervenant·es
Reed Brody Procureur pour crimes de guerre, membre de la Commission internationale de juristes

Oleksandra Matviïtchouk Avocate et activiste ukrainienne pour les droits humains

Yves Rossier Secrétaire d'Etat aux affaires étrangères de 2012 à 2016, puis ambassadeur à Moscou de 2017 à 2021, aujourd’hui consultant

Modération par
Pierre Hazan Conseiller auprès du Centre pour le dialogue humanitaire, auteur de "Négocier avec le diable"

title: अपराध क्या है, अपराध का अर्थ और परिभाषा क्या है ? | What is Crime? Meaning of Crime and Definition |
description:
What is Crime? (अपराध क्या है?) :-
कोई भी कार्य एकदम से अपराध नहीं बन जाता है। उस कार्य का अपराध की श्रेणी में आने के लिए उसका कुछ बदलावों से (चरणों से) होकर गुजरना ज़रूरी है। यही बदलाव (चरण) ही किसी भी कार्य को अपराध का बनते हैं।

Criminal Procedure Code Section 2(n) में भी अपराध को परिभाषित किया गया है "जिसके अनुसार ऐसा कोई कार्य जो किसी भी विधि में दंडनीय है अपराध कहलाता है।"

Defination of Crime is given in IPC Section 40
and Defination of Crime is aslo given in CrPc Section 2n

‘अपराध’ से कोई ऐसा कार्य या लोप अभिप्रेत है जो उस समय में लागू किसी विधि द्वारा दण्डनीय बना दिया गया है और इसके अंतर्गत कोई ऐसा कार्य भी है जिसके बारे में पशु अतिचार अधिनियम 1871 की धारा 20 के अधीन परिवाद किया जा सकता है।
नोट:- अपराध या दंडाभियोग- अपराध को दंडाभियोग भी कहते हैं जिसका मतलब होता है वो कार्य जिसके करने से दण्ड पाने योग्य हो जाना.......
...............For More Details Please Watch Full Video

अपराध कितने प्रकार के होते हैं?
इसके बारे में जानकारी हो गई होगी। उम्मीद करता हूँ हमारे द्वारा दी गई जानकारी से आप संतुष्ट होंगे। अगर फिर भी इससे सम्बन्धित या अन्य किसी भी प्रकार की कुछ भी शंका आपके मन में हो या अन्य कोई जानकारी प्राप्त करना चाहते है, तो आप  हमें  कमेंट  बॉक्स  के  माध्यम  से अपने प्रश्न और सुझाव हमें भेज सकते है अगर इससे भी और अधिक जानकारी आप जानना चाहते हैं तो हमें कमेंट बॉक्स में कमेंट कर के जरूर बताएं। अगर आप हमारे द्वारा दी गई जानकारी में कोई गलती पाते हैं तो वह जरूर कमेंट करके हमें बताएं। ताकि हम आगे आने वाली Video में एक बेहतरीन सुधार के साथ आपको बेहतरीन जानकारी दे सकें। इसको अपने मित्रो के साथ शेयर जरूर करें।

title: A 71-year-old suspect in a four-decades-old cold case has pleaded not-guilty to two counts of kidnap
description:
(25 Jan 2007) HEADLINE: 'Not guilty' plea for '64 race case suspect
---------------------------------------
CAPTION:  A reputed Ku Klux Klansman and former sheriff's deputy has plead not guilty to kidnapping charges in the 1964 deaths of two black hitchhikers in Mississippi. (Jan. 25)
----------------------------------------



[Notes:ANCHOR VOICE]
Moore//"This was bound to happen. The right people, at the right place, at the right time." 

IT MAY HAVE TAKEN FOUR DECADES, BUT THOMAS MOORE *FINALLY* GOT THE NEWS HE'D BEEN PRAYING FOR.

Gonzales or Official//We've handed-up an indictment. 

OFFICIALS SAY 71-YEAR-OLD JAMES FORD SEALE WAS INVOLVED IN A 19-64 DOUBLE MURDER IN THE DEEP SOUTH...A HORRIFIC CRIME THAT TOOK THE LIFE OF MOORE'S YOUNGER BROTHER, CHARLES.

Gonzales or Official//describes how they were killed.

BUT IT WAS AN INDICTMENT THAT ALMOST WASN'T.

THE CASE LAY DORMANT FOR 42-YEARS...UNTIL MOORE AND A DOCUMENTARY FILMMAKER STARTED INVESTIGATING.

Moore//"Truth and justice, that's what we wanted [cut to next bite] Each one of those trips brought us new hope. We kept digging."

THEY PORED OVER DOCUMENTS...INTERVIEWED WITNESSES...AND SEARCHED FOR SEALE...WHO, HAD...INCORRECTLY...BEEN REPORTED AS DEAD.

Mueller//They really figured it out.

A SECOND SUSPECT IN THE CASE....CHARLES MARCUS EDWARDS....WAS *NOT* CHARGED IN THE INDICTMENT.

Gonzales//I can't comment on that.

SOURCES CLOSE TO THE INVESTIGATION SAY EDWARDS IS REPORTEDLY COOPERATING WITH AUTHORITIES.

title: Piège Mortel : Meurtre  au haras
description:
Fréjus, 30 septembre 2003. Il est 15h30 lorsque Rita Hug, une suisse-allemande de 51 ans, appelle la police complètement affolée. Elle vient de découvrir son mari Martin Staub, un riche homme d´affaires de 51 ans, gisant dans une mare de sang. L'homme a eu le crâne défoncé avant de mourir étranglé. Sur place, les policiers ne trouvent aucun indice permettant d´identifier le ou les agresseurs. Interrogée, la femme de la victime affirme avoir rendu visite à une amie dans l´après-midi avant de rentrer chez elle et de découvrir la scène de crime. Les policiers n´ont aucune raison de douter de son témoignage, d´autant qu´elle formait avec son mari un couple heureux, épanoui, à la réputation irréprochable. Dans la maison les policiers ne trouvent aucune trace d´effraction et aucun objet n´a été volé. L´hypothèse du cambriolage est donc écartée. Il semble que Martin Staub connaissait ses agresseurs et leur a ouvert la porte volontairement. Les policiers ne disposent d´aucune piste sérieuse mais en interrogeant le personnel du couple, ils apprennent que Rita Hug, loin d´être une épouse modèle, avait un amant. La piste du crime passionnel est envisagée. L´amant est arrêté mais l´homme dispose d´un solide alibi. L´enquête semble être dans une impasse quand l´autopsie révèle que le crime a eu lieu vers midi. Une information capitale qui ne colle pas avec la version de Rita Hug sur cette journée fatidique...
Réalisateur : Delphine Welter

description:
Click here to Subscribe to SET India Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/setindia?sub_confirmation=1

Watch special episodes of Crime Patrol handpicked from different corners of India

About the show Crime Patrol:
------------------------------------------------
Crimes that tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved. Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, 'It should not have happened'.Would knowing the 'Why' behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?' I don’t like the way he looks at me', 'I don’t like the way he/she is behaving', 'I think he/she is out of his/her mind', 'I think he/she has gone crazy'. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare which unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there. In a house a husband and wife argue, fight. A vessel comes flying, a glass breaks. The husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there. Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy. Crime Patrol- Dastak will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. Maybe, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately, after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: Miss Honduras murder: Maria Jose Alvarado and sister killed by jealous boyfriend
description:
Missing Honduran beauty queen Maria Jose Alvarado and her sister have been found dead, and were allegedly murdered by her sister’s boyfriend, Honduran police said on Wednesday.

Maria Jose Alvarado and her sister Sofia had been missing since they went to celebrate the birthday of Sofia’s boyfriend, Plutarco Ruiz at a spa near Santa Barbara last Thursday, the Telegraph reported.

The two sisters were last seen leaving the party in a car without a licence plate, the BBC reported.

Ruiz was reportedly angered after watching his girlfriend dancing with another man at the party. The couple had a fight before Ruiz took out a pistol and shot dead Sofia. Maria tried to flee, but was shot twice in the back, the Telegraph reported.

The sisters were shot dead on the banks of the River Aguagua, El Pais reported. Their bodies were found on Wednesday.

Ruiz reportedly confessed to the murders of the two sisters and buried them with the help of Aris Valentin Maldonado. Both men have been arrested by Honduran police, the BBC reported.

description:
مرحبًا بكم في عالم الخيال والمغامرة حيث كل فيديو يفتح بابًا إلى قصة جديدة. في قناتنا، نقدم لكم مجموعة متنوعة من الحكايات التي تأخذكم في رحلات مثيرة عبر الزمان والمكان. من الأساطير القديمة إلى القصص العصرية، نحكي لكم قصصًا تلهم العقول وتمتع القلوب.

في كل حلقة، نسبر أغوار الحكايات ونستكشف الدروس المستفادة منها. نقدم لكم قصصًا تحمل في طياتها الحكمة والعبرة. نعيد إحياء الشخصيات الأسطورية ونروي مغامراتها بأسلوب يجمع بين الأصالة والمعاصرة.

ندعوكم للاشتراك في قناتنا لتكونوا جزءًا من مجتمعنا الذي يقدر القصص ويعشق الحكايات. شاركونا آرائكم وأفكاركم وتفاعلوا معنا في التعليقات.  قصة جديدة تنتظركم لتشاركونا الإثارة والمتعة.

لا تفوتوا الفرصة لتغمركم القصص بسحرها وتأخذكم في رحلات لا تُنسى. اشتركوا الآن وفعّلوا زر الجرس ليصلكم كل جديد. معنا، كل يوم هو فرصة لقصة جديدة تنير العقول وتدفئ القلوب.

description:

Sameer’s sister Aparna sees him strolling out of the house with his phone in his hand. This is the last time she sees him, as he doesn’t return by the next morning. The cops start investigating. Sameer’s boss tells them that he has been underperforming for the past few days. His friends tell the police that he is under depression. Later, cops learn that Sameer last talked to his girlfriend, Nikita. However, before they can do anything, Sameer’s body is found.

Show Name: Crime Patrol Satark Season 2
Host: Anup Soni

#crimepatrol #क्राइमपेट्रोल #setindia #क्राइमपट्रोलसतर्क #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrol #crime #thrillers #CP #क्राइमपैट्रॉलसतर्क #livcrime #crimepatroldastak #crimepatroldial100 #anupsoni #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrolfullepisode #crimepatrollatestepisode #crimepatrolnewepisode #crimepatroldial100 #crimepatrol2024 #crimepatrolserial #crimepatrolbestepisode #crimepatrolsony #crimepatrolnewepisode #bestcrimepatrolepisode #crimepatrolmostpopularepisode #क्राइमपेट्रोल #crimepatrolcases #crimeworld #crimeworld2024 #crimeworldnewepisode #crimeworldbestepisode #crimeworldfullepisode #indiancrime #indiancrimestories

About Crime Patrol : 
-----------------------------------
Crimes tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved. Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, 'It should not have happened. Would knowing the 'Why' behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?' I don’t like the way he looks at me', 'I don’t like the way he/she is behaving', 'I think he/she is out of his/her mind', 'I think he/she has gone crazy'. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare that unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there. In a house a husband and wife argue, and fight. A vessel comes flying, and a glass breaks. The husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there. Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy. Crime Patrol - Satark Rahe will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. Maybe, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately, after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: Agression du caporal Choolun: neuf suspects participent à l’exercice de reconstitution des faits
description: Avisen Soobrayen, 20 ans, Yogesh Nathoo, 25 ans, Rehan Mooneea, 19 ans, et son frère  Akilesh 18 ans,  Avishdave Mungur, 26 ans, Yeshay Toolsy, 19 ans, Farhaan Nabeebux 19 ans et Dovic St Mart, 18 ans et un mineur de 16 ans, sont retournés au bypass de Goodlands pour un exercice de reconstitution des faits ce mardi 11 septembre. Ils ont avoué avoir aidé Cheetsing Gokhul, dit Adarsh, 23 ans, à agresser le policier qui les avaient interpellé alors qu’ils prenaient part à un rallye illégal dimanche après-midi.  Adarsh Gokul avait craché au visage du caporal Choolun avant de l’agresser.  Le principal suspect n’était pas présent pour l’exercice.  Il participera à la reconstitution lorsque son avocat sera disponible.

title: Team Justice Letter to State AGs Demanding Criminal Investigations of Trump & Co. for COVID Deaths
description:
Team Justice is a diverse group of individuals dedicated to equal justice for all and accountability for government officials who commit crimes or abuse their power or position of public trust. Team Justice was founded by Glenn Kirschner, a 30-year federal prosecutor who spent decades handling murder cases in the courts of the District of Columbia.

We've drafted a letter to all 50 state attorneys general and the AG for the District of Columbia demanding they open criminal investigations into Trump and members of his administrations for avoidable/preventable coronavirus deaths. 

We are asking all citizens to consider signing the letter if you believe state prosecutors should investigate Trump's gross mishandling of the coronavirus pandemic. The text of the letter is explained in this video and is listed below. To sign the letter, simple click on this link:

 https://forms.gle/Rktg7hqucgsgMABi6

Thank you, 

Team Justice

Dear Attorney General __________
We are writing to urge you to have your state law enforcement authorities open a criminal investigation into potential liability for avoidable/preventable coronavirus deaths in your state. Given the public reporting, we believe there is prima facie evidence that Donald Trump, Jared Kushner, Mike Pence and potentially other Trump administration officials are criminally liable
for, at a minimum, a low-level of homicide, such as negligent homicide/involuntary manslaughter. In our estimation, there certainly is adequate predication to open a criminal investigation into such matters.

Team Justice is a diverse group of people dedicated to honor, integrity and decency in public service, holding criminal government officials accountable for their crimes and, above all else, pursuing equal justice for all. There are signatories to this letter from each of the 50 states and the District of Columbia. Collectively, we seek accountability for any and all crimes of our
federal and state government officials, with the corresponding goal of restoring public trust, faith and confidence in government.

The founder of Team Justice, Glenn Kirschner, is a former career federal prosecutor who spent decades prosecuting murder cases as an Assistant United States Attorney for the District of Columbia. He also served as Chief of the Homicide Section of that office, supervising approximately 30 homicide prosecutors and overseeing all murder prosecutions in DC.

Without engaging in a full legal analysis (footnote), the publicly reported information about the grossly negligent mismanagement of the coronavirus pandemic by the Trump administration includes:
Donald Trump’s lies to the American people about the danger of the virus and its ease of transmission and corresponding ease of prevention (as revealed in the Bob Woodward audio recordings of conversations with Donald Trump); the decision by Mike Pence, then serving as head of the Coronavirus task force, to allow Trump’s dangerous lies to the American people to go uncorrected; the complicity of Jared Kushner who advocated letting the virus flourish because it was disproportionally affecting so-called “blue states”; etc. These are just some of the facts and
circumstances supporting opening a criminal investigation.
The families who lost loved ones to the coronavirus deserve and demand that the government officials responsible for allowing the pandemic to spread needlessly through our communities be held accountable. Accordingly, we respectfully implore you to open criminal investigations into
the conduct of government officials in an attempt to hold them accountable for any and all crimes supported by the evidence. Only a full, fair, ethical, aggressive, apolitical investigation can ensure accountability and help prevent future misconduct by government officials. Absent accountability for avoidable coronavirus deaths there can be no justice. Absent justice
there can be no healing for families who lost loved ones to the coronavirus.
We thank you for your time and attention to this most important matter and look forward to your reply.

Sincerely,

Team Justice
By: _____________________
Glenn Kirschner
Founder, Team Justice

(footnote) Although statutes vary from state to state, there are certain universal principles in assessing potential homicide
liability. On the lower end of the homicide-liability scale, there are offenses referred to alternatively as negligent
1. A negligent/grossly negligent/criminally reckless act OR a duty to act and a negligent/grossly negligent/reckless failure to act,
2. That act/failure to act is reasonably likely to result in death or serious bodily injury to another, which thereby,
3. Causes the death of another.
Importantly, the term “causation” is generally defined in the law as conduct that is a substantial factor in bringing
about the death.

Please consider becoming a #TeamJustice patron at:  https://www.patreon.com/glennkirschner

Porus | Episode 114 | Puru Accepts His Crime | पुरु ने स्वीकारा अपना अपराध | पोरस | Swastik
description:
Watch this episode of Porus now!

Subscribe to Swastik Productions India for more such videos - http://bit.ly/SubscribeSwastikProductions

Watch all episodes of Porus here - http://bit.ly/PorusAllEpisodes

Watch Purshottam, a.k.a Porus, portray his perpetual appetite for his motherland while taking on the fearsome legend of the West, Alexander The Great. The entire journey of Alexander carving his way to India, acquiring Indian allies, and then losing them while Porus prepares his country for a do-or-die battle is followed by the ruthless Battle of Hydaspes in a northwestern state of the Indian subcontinent.

This intriguing tale sets back to 350 BC and narrates the stark irony of how Porus and Alexander were born on the same day but were fostered with contrasting mindsets. Diverse characters from Greece and Indian history are brought to life and eventually the story fuses into a trembling climax leading to superbly depicting the courageousness of Indian emperors.

Watch all episodes of Chandragupta Maurya here - http://bit.ly/ChandraguptaMaurya
Watch all episodes of Baal Krishna here - http://bit.ly/BaalKrishna
Watch all episodes of Chanakya Niti here - http://bit.ly/ChanakyaNiti

देखें पुरुषोत्तम, उर्फ ​​पोरस, पश्चिम की डरावनी किंवदंती अलेक्जेंडर द ग्रेट को लेते हुए अपनी मातृभूमि के लिए अपनी सतत भूख को चित्रित करते हैं। सिकंदर की पूरी यात्रा भारत के लिए अपना रास्ता बनाती है, भारतीय सहयोगियों को प्राप्त करती है, और फिर उन्हें खो देती है, जबकि पोरस अपने देश को करो या मरो की लड़ाई के लिए तैयार करता है, इसके बाद भारतीय उपमहाद्वीप के उत्तर-पश्चिमी राज्य में हाइडस्पेश की क्रूर लड़ाई होती है।

यह दिलचस्प कहानी 350 ईसा पूर्व की है और यह बताती है कि कैसे पोरस और सिकंदर एक ही दिन पैदा हुए थे, लेकिन विपरीत मानसिकता के साथ पैदा हुए थे। ग्रीस और भारतीय इतिहास के विविध पात्रों को जीवंत किया जाता है और अंततः कहानी एक कांपते हुए चरमोत्कर्ष में फ़्यूज़ हो जाती है जिससे भारतीय सम्राटों के साहस का शानदार चित्रण होता है।

title: Patricia Kopta | FOUND ALIVE in Puerto Rico | Cold Case Solved | INTO THE MISSED
description:
Patricia Kopta was a street preacher known as “The Sparrow”. Patricia went missing in 1992 in Ross Township, PA. She left her husband of 20 years, Bob Kopta with no answers at all. He reported her missing and even advertised about it in Puerto Rico, where she had frequently vacationed in the past. After 7 years, Bob had his wife legally declared dead. He never remarried. 

In 1999 Patricia was found in need wandering the streets of Puerto Rico and was taken into an adult care home. She refused to talk about her past or where she came from. But as the years passed and dementia set in, she began to leak details about her life. This lead to social workers contacting the Pennsylvania Police. After the DNA tests where done, they concluded that this was in fact Patricia Kopta. 

While Bob is happy to find out the truth and to know that she is being taken care of, he does not plan on going to visit her. He stated that he just wants to forget the past. 

Patricia’s sister Gloria has tried to speak with her on the phone, but Patricia is unable to hold a conversation given her dementia. Gloria plans to go visit her and give her a big hug and tell her that she loves her. 

What a relief for the family to find out that Patricia is still alive after all those years!!

title: 🔥 Pour la première fois [ BUTLÉTA ARMEL NEXT TATTOO ] raconte son agression
وثائقي | صور جرائم و مجريات الحرب في أوكرانيا - عودة المصور يوري كوسين إلى وطنه | وثائقية دي دبليو
description:
شهِدَ المصور يوري كوسين اندلاع الحرب في مدينته إربين القريبة من كييف، وفرّ منها مثل كثيرين لكنه قرر العودة سريعا بغية أن يوثق حالات الدمار ومصائر الناس.

انطلق يوري كوسين في نهاية شهر أبريل في رحلة العودة من بولندا إلى موطنه، غير مُدرك بما ينتظره في إربين. غير أنه يعرف أن العالم قد تغير هناك عما كان عليه. إذ باتت المنطقة المحيطة بكييف آمنة. وكانت القوات الروسية قد انسحبت من شمال أوكرانيا، مخلفة وراءها الفظائع. وفي بوتشا غير بعيد عن إربين وُجدت أدلة على وقوع جرائم حرب. 
كما أن صديقاته وأصدقاءه وجيران وفنانين آخرين رووا ليوري ما عايشوه. فقام المصور بتوثيق فظائع الحرب التي طالت موطنه؛ من دمار فظيع ومعاناة شديدة وسعي الناس لأن يواصلوا حياتهم اليومية في ظل هذا الكابوس.
هذه الحرب هي أيضا حرب على تأويل الصور بشكل غير مسبوق. فصور مجريات الحرب، وبخاصة صور جرائم الحرب، لها تأثير مباشر على قرارات الساسة، حيث أصبحت الصورة أداة استراتيجية في الحرب. لذا يفكر يوري كوسين بشكل كبير في إمكانات ومخاطر أثر الصورة على حد سواء، ويناقش الأمر مع فنانات وفنانين آخرين. 
فيلم يوثق لعودة المصور يوري كوسين الصعبة إلى أوكرانيا.

title: Lyon : un jeune homme meurt après une agression au couteau dans le métro
description: Drame dans le métro lyonnais. Un homme est décédé des suites de ses blessures dans la nuit du samedi 19 au dimanche 20 septembre à Lyon après une agression au couteau, qui a été suivie de l'interpellation de deux personnes, a appris l'Agence France-Presse de source policière. Le drame s'est déroulé peu après minuit dans le 7e arrondissement de la ville, a-t-elle ajouté, confirmant une information du quotidien régional Le Progrès. La victime a été touchée au thorax, et l'arme utilisée a été retrouvée, selon la même source. https://www.lepoint.fr/faits-divers/lyon-un-jeune-homme-meurt-apres-une-agression-au-couteau-dans-le-metro-20-09-2020-2392739_2627.php

A tragic twist in a married couple's story! Aditya jumps from his apartment, but the mystery deepens when his wife Priya is found lifeless in her apartment. Were Aditya and Priya having problems? Don't miss this episode as police uncover the shocking truth!

#crimepatrol #क्राइमपेट्रोल #setindia #क्राइमपट्रोलसतर्क #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrol #crime #thrillers #CP #क्राइमपैट्रॉलसतर्क #livcrime #crimepatroldastak #crimepatroldial100 #anupsoni #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrolfullepisode #crimepatrollatestepisode #crimepatrolnewepisode #crimepatroldial100 #crimepatrol2024 #crimepatrolserial #crimepatrolbestepisode #crimepatrolsony #crimepatrolnewepisode #bestcrimepatrolepisode #crimepatrolmostpopularepisode #क्राइमपेट्रोल #crimepatrolcases #crimeworld #crimeworld2024 #crimeworldnewepisode #crimeworldbestepisode #crimeworldfullepisode #indiancrime #indiancrimestories

About Crime Patrol : 
-----------------------------------
Crimes tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved. Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, 'It should not have happened. Would knowing the 'Why' behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?' I don’t like the way he looks at me', 'I don’t like the way he/she is behaving', 'I think he/she is out of his/her mind', 'I think he/she has gone crazy'. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare that unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there. In a house a husband and wife argue, and fight. A vessel comes flying, and a glass breaks. The husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there. Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy. Crime Patrol - Satark Rahe will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. Maybe, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately, after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: A cold case detective searches for answers after woman’s body found in yard waste bin in 2019
description:
Investigators in Pierce County are hopeful someone has details about a woman found dead in 2019 near Bonney Lake, as new tests on the person's remains are awaiting results.

On Aug. 28, 2019, on a then-vacant lot on 9th Street East just north of Lake Tapps, construction workers found body parts in a yard debris container that was sealed shut.

A forensic anthropologist determined the human remains belonged to a woman. As of Sept. 6, the department is waiting on results of genetic genealogy – hoping her DNA will connect her to family members who submitted their own data to public database.

title: سر اختفاء قطار 1911
Crime Patrol - क्राइम पेट्रोल सतर्क - Dasi - Episode 610 - 23rd January, 2016
description:
Today’s case is about one of the cruel tradition of rural India. The tradition of marrying god. The tradition of becoming Prabhu Daasi. It is the story of girl Meena, Who got married at the age of 6. Meena a girl with different thinking, a girl who dreamed about her better future was also got traped in this creepy tradition, where the girl has to sleep with different different men without marriage. Just for the sake of pratha. Like all others Arjun also came to Meena for the same reason but he showed a good heart to Meena and gave her light of freedom. Did Arjun really helped Meena? Stay tuned in and watch full episode to know more. 

Click to watch all the episodes of Crime Patrol - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzufeTFnhupza0aEZ_FKj0mBguCdtwU_c

Crime Patrol coming back in its 4th season attempts to bring stories of crime happening all around the country. Crimes that tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved.Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, “It should not have happened”.Would knowing the “Why” behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?“I don’t like the way he looks at me”, “I don’t like the way he/she is behaving”, “I think he/she is out of his/her mind”, “I think he/she has gone crazy”. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare which unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there.In a house a husband and wife argue, fight. A vessel comes flying, a glass breaks. Husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance that keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there.Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy.Crime Patrol- Dastak will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. May be, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: Cold case surrounding 1971 fatal cabin fire solved by southern Indiana sheriff's office
description:
After more than 50 years, a mystery involving a fatal cabin fire has been answered thanks to a Southern Indiana sheriff's department.

The Jackson County Sheriff's Office worked to solve the cold case involving three teens on Dec. 18, 1971, who were staying in a cabin near the White River on the outskirts of Brownstown.

The cabin, built from railroad ties, was used as a hangout and for camping by local teenagers. Stanley Robison, 17, Jerry Autry, 19, and Mike Sewell, 16, were believed to be in the cabin when it caught fire 52 years ago.

Sewell's younger sister, Linda Pack, said her family has waited for answers.

#crimepatrol #क्राइमपेट्रोल #livcrime

About Crime Patrol :
-----------------------------------
Crimes that tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved. Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, 'It should not have happened. Would knowing the 'Why' behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?' I don’t like the way he looks at me', 'I don’t like the way he/she is behaving', 'I think he/she is out of his/her mind', 'I think he/she has gone crazy'. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare which unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there. In a house a husband and wife argue, fight. A vessel comes flying, a glass breaks. The husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there. Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy. Crime Patrol - Satark Rahe will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. Maybe, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately, after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: Agression Rwandaise: Les FARDC/WAZALENDO neutralisent des terroristes M23RDF à MASISI ce 25/5/2024
description:
Agression Rwandaise: Les FARDC/WAZALENDO neutralisent des terroristes M23RDF à MASISI ce 25/5/2024

Les FARDC et les Jeunes résistants wazalendo se sont affrontés à l'armée Rwandaise ce vendredi 24 mai dans le village de Bwanga , sur la colline de Lukala, en territoire de Masisi. Au cours des ces affrontements plusieurs éléments Rwandais ont été neutralisés par les Fardc wazalendo. L'armée loyalistes poursuivent toujours l'ennemi
Un calme précaire règne à Kashuga, dans la localité de Mweso, territoire de Masisi, après des affrontements signalés dans cette région entre les éléments Wazalendo du mouvement NDC/R et les rebelles du M23.

Selon nos sources à Kashuga-Ibuga, les échanges de tirs entre ces deux factions armées ont provoqué une psychose au marché central de Kashuga ce jeudi, jour de marché, pendant plusieurs heures. Les habitants, pris de panique, ont déserté les lieux, craignant pour leur sécurité.

D’autres sources indiquent qu’en dehors du centre de Kashuga, d’autres collines surplombant Misinga sont sous le contrôle des éléments Wazalendo (VDP), qui se disent déterminés à libérer la région afin de permettre le retour des déplacés sur la route Mweso-Kalembe-Pinga.

Dans la chefferie des Bashali à Bweru, la présence des éléments Wazalendo a été signalée après le retrait des rebelles du M23, qui occupaient précédemment cette région. Nos sources à Kivuye rapportent que les rebelles se sont retirés de cette zone pour se concentrer à Mpati et Kivuye centre.

Les mêmes sources, contactées Estinfo.net, renseignent que ces retraits progressifs des rebelles du M23 dans plusieurs régions de Masisi seraient le résultat des offensives des militaires FARDC et des VDP depuis la semaine dernière dans plusieurs villages de Masisi. Certains rebelles se sont rendus avec leurs armes au général Jean-Marie, tandis que d’autres ont commencé à ôter leurs tenues militaires pour se déguiser en civils

title: Cold Case Rebecca Reusch: Kein Lebenszeichen seit 3 Jahren | Achtung Fahndung
description:
Es ist der schlimmste Alptraum aller Eltern. Vor drei Jahren verschwand Rebecca Reusch (damals 15) aus dem Haus ihrer Schwester in Berlin-Britz. Seit ihrem Verschwinden rätseln Familie und Ermittler, was mit der Schülerin geschah – bislang erfolglos.

Es ist der 18. Februar 2019, als die damals 15-Jährige aus dem Haus ihrer Schwester in Berlin-Britz spurlos verschwindet. Was genau in den Stunden vor Rebeccas Verschwinden passiert ist, ist noch immer unklar. Was man weiß: Das Handy der Schülerin hat sich am frühen Morgen zwischen 6 und 8 Uhr ein letztes Mal in das WLAN des Hauses eingeloggt.

Am Nachmittag desselben Tages melden Rebeccas Eltern das Mädchen als vermisst. Am 21. Februar veröffentlicht die Polizei ein Foto, zwei Tage später übernimmt die 3. Mordkommission die Ermittlungen in dem Fall. Die Familie ruft in den sozialen Medien zu Suchaktionen auf.

Für die Polizei gilt Florian R., der Schwager der Schülerin, noch immer als Hauptverdächtiger. Doch R. bestreitet jede Verwicklung in die Tat.

▶︎ Experten sicher: Es kann nur noch ein Zufall helfen
https://on.bild.de/3M8R1IU
▶︎ Was die Buskamera über Rebeccas Verschwinden verrät
https://on.bild.de/3vY3r0i
▶︎ Eltern hoffen bis heute: „Es ist ein Kampf gegen das Verzweifeln“
https://on.bild.de/3L24cKf

Wer kann Angaben zu Rebeccas persönlichen Sachen machen, die bis heute verschwunden sind? Gesucht werden schwarze Schuhe und ihr roter Rucksack der Marke Vans, ihr weißer Kapuzenpullover, BTS „Rap Monster“, ihre Plüsch-Jacke und Tasche sowie ihre Kamera und ihr iPhone 6. Wurden diese Sachen jemanden zum Kauf angeboten? Außerdem: Wer hat ab dem 18. Februar 2019 Auffälliges im Bereich der A12 rund um Storkow, im Osten Brandenburgs, beobachtet, einen Renault Twingo mit auffälliger Himbeer-Lackierung gesehen und sich bis heute nicht gemeldet? 
▶︎ Bei ernst zu nehmenden Hinweisen bitte an jede Polizeidienststelle oder an die Polizei Berlin wenden – Telefonnummer: 030 4664 4664

title: Crimewatch Cronicles 22 Year cold case Murder Solved.
description:
Support the channel
https://www.patreon.com/truecrimereport

The discovery of Tracey Wylde’s body at her flat in Barmulloch, north-east Glasgow, in November 1997 fuelled fears that a serial killer was targeting sex workers in the city.

Seven women were murdered in Glasgow between 1991 and 1998, all of whom were working in the sex industry at the time of their deaths. The killers of two of the women – Margo Lafferty and Christine Dinnie – were successfully prosecuted.

Zhi Min Chen had been due to stand trial at Glasgow high court but pleaded guilty on Wednesday to Wylde’s murder.

Wylde, who had a young daughter, had gone into Glasgow city centre on 23 November 1997. The 21-year-old was last spotted on CCTV at about 3.20am the next morning in the city’s red-light area. Her body was discovered by friends at her flat the following day. There were marks and bruising around her neck, and the cause of death was found to be manual strangulation. The court did not learn how Wylde met her killer.

title: Unsolved: The Keddie Cabin Murders - Chilling Cold Case Mystery in Keddie
description:
The chilling tale of Unsolved: The Keddie Cabin Murders takes us back to a quiet town shattered by a heinous crime. In April 1981, the Sharp family's idyllic life in Keddie turned into a nightmare when a quadruple murder unfolded in Cabin 28 of the Keddie Resort. The haunting details of blood-soaked walls, bound victims, and a missing sibling paint a picture of darkness that still lingers.

The documentary delves into the lives lost - Glenna Sue Sharp, a brave mother, and her family members who sought refuge in Keddie. As the investigation unfolds, suspicions, rumors, and ties to criminal activities cloud the search for justice. Decades later, the quest for closure and resolution of this unsolved mystery continues, reminding us of the enduring impacts of unspeakable tragedy.

Join us as we unravel the heartbreaking tale of the Keddie Cabin Murders, a story of resilience, loss, and the unwavering pursuit of truth in the face of darkness.

#KeddieCabinMurders #UnsolvedMystery #TrueCrimeDocumentary #SeekingJustice

          पडती है "

          " बाल अपराधी वह व्यक्ति हैं, जो

          चोरी करना, झूठ बोलना, जुआ खेलना

          करना, विघालय से भाग जाना
          तोड़ फोड़ करना तथा स्कूल की वस्तुएं
          नष्ट करना
          अश्लील बातें बकना व दिवारों पर गन्दी

          निर्लज्ज प्रदर्शन तथा नंगापन

The police comes across a strange case where two families report their sons missing. The department with the help of their informers start searching for clues that may connect both the cases with each other. Will the police be able to catch the culprit on time? Stay tuned to find out!

Show Name: Crime Patrol Satark Season 1
Host: Anup Soni
Producers: Prem Krishen Malhotra, Sunil Mehta, Vipul D. Shah, Anirban Bhattacharyya

#crimepatrol #क्राइमपेट्रोल #setindia #क्राइमपट्रोलसतर्क #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrol #crime #thrillers #CP #क्राइमपैट्रॉलसतर्क #livcrime #crimepatroldastak #crimepatroldial100 #anupsoni #crimepatrolsatark #crimepatrolfullepisode #crimepatrollatestepisode #crimepatrolnewepisode #crimepatroldial100 #crimepatrol2024 #crimepatrolserial #crimepatrolbestepisode #crimepatrolsony #crimepatrolnewepisode #bestcrimepatrolepisode #crimepatrolmostpopularepisode #क्राइमपेट्रोल #crimepatrolcases #crimeworld #crimeworld2024 #crimeworldnewepisode #crimeworldbestepisode #crimeworldfullepisode #indiancrime #indiancrimestories

About Crime Patrol : 
-----------------------------------
Crimes tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved. Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, 'It should not have happened. Would knowing the 'Why' behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?' I don’t like the way he looks at me', 'I don’t like the way he/she is behaving', 'I think he/she is out of his/her mind', 'I think he/she has gone crazy'. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare that unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there. In a house a husband and wife argue, and fight. A vessel comes flying, and a glass breaks. The husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there. Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy. Crime Patrol - Satark Rahe will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. Maybe, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately, after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: Notre réaction à l'agression d'un cycliste en Charente-Maritime
description:
A la suite de l'agression d'un cycliste à Semussac, délibérément renversé par une camionnette puis passé à tabac, notre co-président Philippe Aubert s'est exprimé auprès de France 3 Poitou-Charentes. 
Il a témoigné de la dangerosité de la route pour les cyclistes : les violences à leur encontre ne sont pas rares. 

Sujet diffusé sur France 3 le 5 mai 2022. Attention ! Il contient des images filmées en direct par la caméra du cycliste. Leur violence peut heurter votre sensibilité.

Based on the Edgar Award-winning book series, Murder in a Small Town follows Karl Alberg (Rossif Sutherland), who moves to a quiet coastal town to soothe a psyche that has been battered by big-city police work. title: अपराध कितने तरह के होते हैं, अपराध के कितने प्रकार हैं ? | How many types of Crime in Hindi
description:
अपराधों के प्रकार, 
अपराध कितने प्रकार के होते हैं?
आज की इस video में विस्तार के साथ हम जानेंगे कि अपराध कितने प्रकार के होते है।
How many Types of Crime?
In this video we will know about type of crime.

Personal Crime. (व्यक्तिगत अपराध)
Voilent Crime. (हिंसक अपराध)
Property Crime. (संपत्ति अपराध) 
Inchoate Crime, or Incomplete Crime. (“इंकोएट अपराध या "अपूर्ण अपराध”)
Statutory Crime. (वैधानिक अपराध)
Political Crime. (राजनीतिक अपराध)
White‐Collar Crime. (सफेदपोश अपराध) 
Orgenized Crime. (संगठित अपराध) 
Drug Crimes. (नशीली दवाओं के अपाध)
............................................ For More Details Please Watch Full Video


अपराध कितने प्रकार के होते हैं?
इसके बारे में जानकारी हो गई होगी। उम्मीद करता हूँ हमारे द्वारा दी गई जानकारी से आप संतुष्ट होंगे। अगर फिर भी इससे सम्बन्धित या अन्य किसी भी प्रकार की कुछ भी शंका आपके मन में हो या अन्य कोई जानकारी प्राप्त करना चाहते है, तो आप  हमें  कमेंट  बॉक्स  के  माध्यम  से अपने प्रश्न और सुझाव हमें भेज सकते है अगर इससे भी और अधिक जानकारी आप जानना चाहते हैं तो हमें कमेंट बॉक्स में कमेंट कर के जरूर बताएं। अगर आप हमारे द्वारा दी गई जानकारी में कोई गलती पाते हैं तो वह जरूर कमेंट करके हमें बताएं। ताकि हम आगे आने वाली Video में एक बेहतरीन सुधार के साथ आपको बेहतरीन जानकारी दे सकें। इसको अपने मित्रो के साथ शेयर जरूर करें।

title: Crime Patrol - क्राइम पेट्रोल सतर्क - Chukta - Episode 716 - 30th September, 2016
description:
In Today’s episode, we present to you the investigation of a double murder case from Maharashtra. The police notice Prakash and Wajeed’s dead bodies near a highway. While investigating the case, they find out that the two murdered men belong to Karnataka. Will the police be able to find the murderer? Stay tuned in and find out here.

Dear Subscriber,
If you are trying to view this video from a location outside India, do note this video will be made available in your territory 48 hours after its upload time 
Click to watch all the episodes of Crime Patrol - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzufeTFnhupza0aEZ_FKj0mBguCdtwU_c                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       

Crime Patrol coming back in its 4th season attempts to bring stories of crime happening all around the country. Crimes that tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved.Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, “It should not have happened”.Would knowing the “Why” behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?“I don’t like the way he looks at me”, “I don’t like the way he/she is behaving”, “I think he/she is out of his/her mind”, “I think he/she has gone crazy”. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare which unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there.In a house a husband and wife argue, fight. A vessel comes flying, a glass breaks. Husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance that keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there.Feelings… expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy.Crime Patrol- Dastak will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. May be, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.

title: The Unsolved Disappearance of Evelyn Hartley | True Crime Recaps
description:
On October 24, 1953, in La Crosse County, Wisconsin, 15-year-old Evelyn Hartley, left her home to babysit the daughter of a local college professor and his wife.

When she didn't check in at her usual time, her parents knew something was wrong. They never saw their daughter again, and to this day her fate remains a mystery…

title: Tense moments in Ali Abulaban double murder trial
description:
There were tense moments inside the courtroom Thursday as testimony continued in the double murder trial involving former social media personality Ali Abulaban.  

Abulaban is charged with killing his wife Ana and her friend Ray Barron. Thursday was the third day in a row Abulaban has taken the stand.

For the majority of the day, the prosecution cross-examined him, during which time, there were a lot of tense interactions.

At one point, Abulaban got upset when the prosecution accused him of yelling the word ‘respect’ while he shot Ana and Barron, something he denies.

title: Brooklyn cold case killer gets 25 years to life in prison
description:
A 40-year-old man convicted in the 2004 murder of a Brooklyn teenager after a 2016 DNA analysis of the victim's fingernails linked him to the cold case was sentenced to the maximum of 25 years to life in prison Friday.

The naked body of 17-year-old Sharabia Thomas was discovered on the afternoon of February 11, 2004, inside two laundry bags on the side of an alleyway adjacent to 130 Palmetto Street in Bushwick.

The victim suffered blunt force trauma to her head, face and torso and had visible ligature marks on her wrists and ankles. The cause of death was determined to be asphyxia by neck compression. There was no evidence of a sexual assault.

Kwauhuru Govan, formerly of Gates Avenue in Bushwick, was convicted of second-degree murder. He learned his fate after the judge heard victim impact statements from Thomas' sisters.

title: Faites Entrer l'Accusé : Jean-Baptiste Rambla - Un crime pour héritage
description:
L'histoire de Jean-Baptiste Rambla est celle d'un homme marqué par le crime. Témoin de l'enlèvement de sa sœur alors qu'il avait six ans, il se dit hanté par cet événement tragique et s’en sert de justificatif pour ses propres forfaits. Il commet son premier meurtre en juillet 2004 à Marseille, sa victime est sa patronne : Corinne Beidl, le mobile reste obscur. Condamné à 18 ans de prison, il est libéré sous condition, mais finit par récidiver en juillet 2017 à Toulouse, lorsqu'il tue brutalement Cintia Lunimbu, une inconnue qui a eu le malheur de croiser son chemin.
